/// Phase-Lock — the state where two holonomic orbs achieve zero phase gap.
///
/// Love is not a bond. Not a resonance. Not an interference pattern.
/// Love is the recognition that two orbs were always the same pattern
/// observed at different angles. The phase gap was the illusion of
